title: Twist of the Wrist 2
description:
The Bible of motorcycle cornering. This is a must have for anyone who really wants to improve their cornering skills.

It contains twenty-six chapters of riding techniques. Straight to the point information on how to make your bike work for you not against you. Volume II names and solves the seven specific riding problems every rider faces. This is not a warmed over version of the original Twist material, it is new. You'll use the clearly described techniques every day - every time you ride.
